org.matsim.core.mobsim.qsim.qnetsimengine

Interface QLinkI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Customizable, MatsimExtensionPoint, MatsimNetworkObject, NetsimLink, TimeVariantLink, VisLink
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QLinkImpl, QLinkLanesImpl

    public interface QLinkI
extends NetsimLink, TimeVariantLink
    Contains all the logic for the QLinks which make up the QNetwork.

    One can argue that the QNetsimEngine could treat more general links than just "queues". However, in the end they live with "(qlane.)addFromUpstream" and "(qlane.)addFromUpstream", which is quite restricted, since it does not pass the velocity. Not passing the velocity means that it cannot be used for more general mobsims.
    Author:
    nagel
